<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīmatturyyanṛsiṁhyabhutāḷapatēcāturthakēṁkē ghaṭāmā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>sē ca sitapaṁcamīgurudinē svapnēsvarasya priĀ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> sītā kummā 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>vibhōrakhaṁḍita mahādīpasyatai I lāḍḍaka<unclear>ṁ</unclear> <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> �ātuṁ viṁssati māḍa
<lb n="4" break="no"/>kāṁccenāmadāt bhaṁḍāragēhē sadā <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīkū<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>mmadēvasya pura pra
<lb n="5" break="no"/>timāṁ dīpadaruṇīṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> svapnesvarapriyā sīta prādādācaṁdratāra
<lb n="6" break="no"/>kaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>śakava<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>ṣaṁbulu 1302 Agunēṁṭi (<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>) vīraśrīnarasiṁhya
<lb n="7" break="no"/>dēvarā pravarddhamānavijayarājyasaṁvvātsaraṁbulu 40 ka srāhi kuṁ
<lb n="8" break="no"/>bha kṛṣṇa 5 guruvarāna <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> kaḷiṁgaparīkṣa mahāpātra śrīsvapnēśvara
<lb n="9" break="no"/>jiyyanaṁgāri bhāryya śrīsītādēvi tamaku Āyuṣkāmyartthamu
<lb n="10" break="no"/>gānu śrīkurmanāthuni divyasanidhini Akhaṁḍadīpānaku prātidina
<lb n="11" break="no"/>munu Aḍyaṁḍēsi nunyakunu śrīkūrmmanātthuni śrībhaṁḍārānaku padmani
<lb n="12" break="no"/>dhipeṭina gaṁḍamādalu 20 dīpasahitaṁgā pratima 1 Ī dharmma
<lb n="13" break="no"/>muceliṁpanu tirupati śrīvaiṣṇavarakṣaḥ (<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>) svadattadviguṇaṁ pu
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ṇyaṁ paradattānupālanaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> varadattāpahārēṇa svadattaṁ niṣphalaṁ bha
<lb n="15" break="no"/>vēt śrī śrī śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

